Backup DB:
mysqldump -u limih -p0}y3V7SJEi limih_ws_db > /limdata/mysql_dump_test/limih_ws_db.sql

Drop DB:
mysql -uroot -plimXmim -e "DROP DATABASE limih_ws_db;"

Reload DB:
/limdata/limih/mimTools/adminbin/setup_ws_mysql.sh

Restore a database:
mysql -h localhost -u limih -p0}y3V7SJEi limih_ws_db < /limdata/mysql_dump_test/limih_ws_db.sql


[From setup_ws_mysql.sh] Create limih user on mysql:
mysql -h localhost -uroot -plimXmim limih_ws_db -e "create user 'limih'@'localhost' identified by '0}y3V7SJEi';"
Grant Permissions to limih:
mysql -h localhost -uroot -plimXmim limih_ws_db -e "grant all on limih_ws_db.* to 'limih'@'localhost';"
